name: ostd::task::scheduler::info::AtomicCpuId::set_if_is_none
src:
pub fn set_if_is_none(&self, cpu_id: CpuId) -> core::result::Result<(), CpuId> {
        self.0
            .compare_exchange(
                Self::NONE,
                cpu_id.into(),
                Ordering::Relaxed,
                Ordering::Relaxed,
            )
            .map(|_| ())
            .map_err(|prev| (prev as usize).try_into().unwrap())
    }
